---
import { BrainCircuit, CircuitBoard, GitMerge, Bot } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-gray-950">
    <div
        class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-indigo-900/10 to-transparent pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500/20 text-sm text-yellow-400 mb-6"
                >
                    <span
                        class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500 animate-pulse"
                    ></span>
                    Coming Soon
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
                    <span class="text-white">Agentic Mode</span>
                    <span class="block text-gray-500 text-2xl mt-2 font-normal"
                        >Autonomous. Intelligent. Capable.</span
                    >
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                    The future of development is agentic. Maverick will soon be
                    able to plan, execute, and correct complex tasks completely
                    autonomously.
                </p>

                <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div
                        class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10"
                    >
                        <Bot class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-400 mb-3" />
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                            Autonomous Execution
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                            Give a goal, and Maverick handles the rest.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10"
                    >
                        <CircuitBoard class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400 mb-3" />
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                            Tool Chaining
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                            Intelligently combines CLI tools to solve problems.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10"
                    >
                        <BrainCircuit class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400 mb-3" />
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                            Long-term Memory
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                            Remembers context across sessions and projects.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10"
                    >
                        <GitMerge class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400 mb-3" />
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                            Strategic Planning
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
                            Breaks down users' requests into actionable steps.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="lg:w-1/2 relative">
                <div
                    class="relative rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-xl p-8 overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-white/[0.02] [mask-image:linear-gradient(0deg,white,transparent)]"
                    >
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-6 font-mono text-sm">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 opacity-50">
                            <div class="min-w-8 text-gray-500">USER</div>
                            <div class="text-gray-300">
                                "Refactor the authentication flow to use JWTs
                                and add Google OAuth."
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="min-w-8 text-indigo-400">AGENT</div>
                            <div class="text-indigo-300">
                                <div class="mb-2">
                                    I will break this down into 3 phases:
                                </div>
                                <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
                                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                        <span class="text-green-400">✓</span>
                                        <span
                                            >1. Install passport-google-oauth20</span
                                        >
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                        <span
                                            class="text-yellow-400 animate-pulse"
                                            >⟳</span
                                        >
                                        <span
                                            >2. Update User schema for provider
                                            ID</span
                                        >
                                    </div>
                                    <div
                                        class="flex items-center gap-2 opacity-50"
                                    >
                                        <span class="text-gray-600">○</span>
                                        <span>3. Create new auth routes</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div
                            class="flex items-start gap-4 mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-white/5"
                        >
                            <div class="min-w-8 text-green-400">EXEC</div>
                            <div
                                class="text-gray-300 bg-black/50 p-3 rounded border border-white/5 w-full"
                            >
                                > npm install passport passport-google-oauth20<br
                                />
                                <span class="text-gray-500"
                                    >... added 2 packages</span
                                >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
